.staging.agilebrazil.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/6413316951_cf6c36bcfe_b1-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"6413316951_cf6c36bcfe_b\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-247\" /></a>\r\n\r\nThe event is going for 5th edition in 2014 and will be held in Florianopolis, Santa Catarina. Each edition of the event attracted hundreds of participants of the Brazilian technology scene and many internationally renowned speakers.\r\n\r\nAgile methods are increasingly being adopted by private and public companies. Agencies and government of some countries, such as Brazil, the United States and England, reporting initiatives agility.\r\n\r\nIn 2014, the Agile Brazil becomes the first official conference of the Agile Alliance outside the U.S., having become the most important conference of agile methods in the southern hemisphere.\r\n\r\n','About','','publish','open','open','','about','','','2014-05-12 03:26:28','2014-05-12 03:26:28','',0,'http://2014.staging.agilebrazil.com/?page_id=13',0,'page','',0),(14,1,'2014-02-21 00:40:47','2014-02-21 00:40:47','Aayla antilles carondian skywalker omwati joruus ferroans. Carnor chommell zev sabé fode jar. Nal rishii conan carlist obi-wan teevan. Ithorian gungan ev-9d9 frozarns aruzan jinn zhell boba yaddle. Mace ord maul ewok mimbanite boltrunians naboo isard t\'landa. Quence shawda maul kamino kwa moff priapulin sebulba. Isolder utapau vau jar mayagil. Watto chirrpa charal yowza lorth jagged. Tarasin hoojib daala ailyn vong metalorn ogemite jango subterrel. Kalee klatooinian irek organa ahsoka trioculus.','About','','inherit','open','open','','13-revision-v1','','','2014-02-21 00:40:47','2014-02-21 00:40:47','',13,'http://2014.staging.agilebrazil.com/uncategorized/13-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(15,1,'2014-02-21 00:41:01','2014-02-21 00:41:01','Located on the Santa Catarina\'s island, Florianópolis, the state capital, is one of the most beautiful cities in the country.\r\n\r\n<a href=\"http://2014.staging.agileb