n-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(302,1,'2014-05-12 03:25:03','2014-05-12 03:25:03','Agile Brazil is the most relevant conference regarding Agile Development Methodologies in Brazil. This is a nonprofit conference made by agile specialists from all regions of Brazil, sharing the same goal: foster and spread Agile culture all over Brazil.\n\n<a href=\"http://2014.staging.agilebrazil.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/6413316951_cf6c36bcfe_b1.jpg\"><img src=\"http://2014.staging.agilebrazil.com/wp-content/uploads/2014/02/6413316951_cf6c36bcfe_b1-300x199.jpg\" alt=\"6413316951_cf6c36bcfe_b\" width=\"300\" height=\"199\" class=\"aligncenter size-medium wp-image-247\" /></a>\n\nO evento está indo para a sua 5ª edição em 2014 e será realizado em Florianópolis, Santa Catarina. Cada edição do evento reuniu centenas de participantes do cenário de tecnologia brasileiro e diversos palestrantes de renome internacional.\n\nMétodos ágeis vêm sendo cada vez mais adotados por empresas privadas e públicas. Agências e órgãos de Governo de alguns países, como Brasil, Estados Unidos e Inglaterra, reportam iniciativas de agilidade.\n\nEm 2014, o Agile Brazil torna-se a primeira conferência oﬁcial da Agile Alliance fora dos EUA, tendo tornado-se a conferência de métodos ágeis mais relevante do hemisfério sul.\n\nThe event is going for 5th edition in 2014 and will be held in Florianopolis, Santa Catarina. Each edition of the event attracted hundreds of participants of the Brazilian technology scene and many internationally renowned speakers.\n\nAgile methods are increasingly being adopted by private and public companies. Agencies and government of some countries, such as Brazil, the United States and England, reporting initiatives agility.','About','','inherit','open','open','','13-autosave-v1','','','2014-05-12 03:25:03','2014-05-12 03:25:03','',13,'http://2014.staging.agilebrazil.com/uncategorized/13-autosave-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(303,1,'2014-05-12 03:26:28','2014-05-12 03:26:28','Agile Brazil 